### 实践四：定期备份策略

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# redis_cluster_backup.sh

BACKUP_DIR="/backup/redis"
DATE=$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S)
PASSWORD="YourStrongPassword123"

# 主节点列表
MASTER_NODES=(
  "192.168.1.101:6379"
  "192.168.1.102:6379"
  "192.168.1.103:6379"
)

mkdir -p $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE

echo "=== Redis Cluster Backup ==="

for master in "${MASTER_NODES[@]}"; do
  HOST=$(echo $master | awk -F: ''{print $1}'')
  PORT=$(echo $master | awk -F: ''{print $2}'')
  
  echo "Backing up $master..."
  
  # 触发 RDB 备份
  redis-cli -h $HOST -p $PORT -a $PASSWORD BGSAVE
  
  # 等待备份完成
  sleep 5
  
  # 复制备份文件
  ssh root@$HOST "cp /data/redis/data/dump.rdb $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE/dump-$HOST-$PORT.rdb"
  
  # 复制 AOF 文件
  ssh root@$HOST "cp /data/redis/data/appendonly.aof $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE/aof-$HOST-$PORT.aof"
done

echo "✅ Backup completed: $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE"

# 清理旧备份（保留7天）
find $BACKUP_DIR -type d -mtime +7 -exec rm -rf {} +
```

---

### 实践五：监控指标

#### 关键监控指标

| 指标 | 说明 | 告警阈值 |
|------|------|---------|
| `cluster_state` | 集群状态 | fail 时告警 |
| `cluster_slots_ok` | 正常槽位数量 | < 16384 时告警 |
| `cluster_known_nodes` | 已知节点数量 | < 6 时告警 |
| `connected_clients` | 连接客户端数 | 接近 maxclients 时告警 |
| `used_memory` | 已用内存 | > 80% maxmemory 时告警 |
| `instantaneous_ops_per_sec` | 当前 QPS | 根据业务设定 |
| `slowlog` | 慢查询数量 | 有慢查询时告警 |

#### 监控脚本

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# cluster_monitor.sh

HOST="192.168.1.101"
PORT="6379"
PASSWORD="YourStrongPassword123"

# 获取关键指标
redis-cli -h $HOST -p $PORT -a $PASSWORD INFO | grep -E "connected_clients|used_memory|instantaneous_ops_per_sec"

# 检查慢查询
redis-cli -h $HOST -p $PORT -a $PASSWORD SLOWLOG GET 10

# 检查集群状态
redis-cli -h $HOST -p $PORT -a $PASSWORD CLUSTER INFO
```

