### 测试集群功能

```bash
# 连接集群并写入数据
redis-cli -c -h 192.168.1.101 -p 6379 -a YourStrongPassword123

# -c 参数：自动路由到正确的节点

# 写入数据
127.0.0.1:6379> SET user:1001 "Alice"
-> Redirected to slot [12539] located at 192.168.1.102:6379
OK

127.0.0.1:6379> SET user:1002 "Bob"
-> Redirected to slot [12540] located at 192.168.1.102:6379
OK

127.0.0.1:6379> SET product:1 "iPhone"
OK

# 读取数据
127.0.0.1:6379> GET user:1001
"Alice"

127.0.0.1:6379> GET product:1
"iPhone"

# 查看集群槽位映射
127.0.0.1:6379> CLUSTER KEYSLOT user:1001
(integer) 12539
```

