## 运维管理

### 扩容：添加主节点

```bash
# 步骤1：准备新节点（192.168.1.107）
# 安装 Redis 并启动（同前）

# 步骤2：将新节点加入集群
redis-cli --cluster add-node \
  192.168.1.107:6379 \
  192.168.1.101:6379 \
  -a YourStrongPassword123

# 步骤3：重新分配槽位
redis-cli --cluster reshard \
  192.168.1.101:6379 \
  -a YourStrongPassword123

# 输入要迁移的槽位数量（16384 / 4 = 4096）
How many slots do you want to move? 4096

# 输入新节点 ID
What is the receiving node ID? <new-node-id>

# 输入源节点 ID（all 表示从所有主节点迁移）
Source node #1: all

# 确认迁移
Do you want to proceed with the proposed reshard plan? yes

# 步骤4：为新主节点添加从节点（192.168.1.108）
redis-cli --cluster add-node \
  192.168.1.108:6379 \
  192.168.1.101:6379 \
  --cluster-slave \
  --cluster-master-id <new-node-id> \
  -a YourStrongPassword123
```

---

### 缩容：删除节点

```bash
# 步骤1：迁移槽位到其他节点
redis-cli --cluster reshard \
  192.168.1.101:6379 \
  -a YourStrongPassword123

# 输入要迁移的槽位数量（该节点的所有槽位）
How many slots do you want to move? <slots-count>

# 输入接收节点 ID
What is the receiving node ID? <target-node-id>

# 输入源节点 ID（要删除的节点）
Source node #1: <node-to-remove-id>

# 确认迁移
Do you want to proceed with the proposed reshard plan? yes

# 步骤2：删除节点
redis-cli --cluster del-node \
  192.168.1.101:6379 \
  <node-id> \
  -a YourStrongPassword123

# 步骤3：停止并清理节点
redis-cli -h <node-ip> -p 6379 -a YourStrongPassword123 SHUTDOWN NOSAVE
```

